  "function_id": "alg_034_expand_mask",
  "name": "ExpandMask",
  "label": "Algorithm 34",
  "page_start": 38,
  "page_end": 38,
  "inputs": [
    {
      "name": "rho",
      "type": "byte_array",
      "description": "seed"
    },
    {
      "name": "mu",
      "type": "int",
      "description": "counter input"
    }
  ],
  "outputs": [
    {
      "name": "y",
      "type": "vector",
      "description": "sampled mask vector"
    }
  ],
  "body_raw": [
    "𝑐 ← 1 + bitlen (𝛾1 − 1) ▷ 𝛾1 is always a power of",
    "for 𝑟 from 0 to ℓ − 1 do",
    "𝜌′ ← 𝜌||IntegerToBytes(𝜇 + 𝑟, 2)",
    "𝑣 ← H(𝜌′, 32𝑐) ▷ seed depends on 𝜇 + 𝑟",
    "𝐲[𝑟] ← BitUnpack(𝑣, 𝛾1 − 1, 𝛾1)",
    "end for",
    "return 𝐲"
  ]
}